OL,3,C'No plans' to strip contract for Parc
OL,4,CPrison from security firm G4S
OL,6,FThe UK Government's Prisons Minister
OL,7,Fhas said he has no plans to strip the
OL,8,Fcontract for running Parc Prison near
OL,9,FBridgend from the security firm G4S.
OL,11,FThe privately-run prison has been the
OL,12,Ffocus of concerns after the death of
OL,13,F17 inmates over the course of 2024.
OL,14,FNot all of the deaths are thought to
OL,15,Fhave been drug-related but eight have
OL,16,Fbeen categorised as from 'non-natural
OL,17,Fcauses.'
