OL,6,FHe said he'd been impressed by
OL,7,Fimprovements on a recent visit and
OL,8,Fwasn't intending to remove the
OL,9,Fcontract.
OL,11,F"I am of the same mind. As I mentioned
OL,12,Fbefore. I've seen a number of prisons
OL,13,Fover the years, both in private
OL,14,Fownership and public ownership, and it
OL,15,Fcomes down to leadership and focus and
OL,16,Fthe way that the prison is run over a
OL,17,Flong period of time.
