OL,3,C'No plans' to strip contract for Parc
OL,4,CPrison from security firm G4S
OL,6,F"And despite the challenges, I think
OL,7,Fthey did a lot of good things at HMP
OL,8,FParc, and I think the reasons why you
OL,9,Fwould close on a contracs, they're not
OL,10,Fthe reasons that I saw on my visit.
OL,12,F"But we are always keeping a close eye
OL,13,Fon what is happening in all of our
OL,14,Fprivate prisons, and we will hold the
OL,15,Fteam to account whether areas that we
OL,16,Fare concerned with."
OL,18,FLord Timpson also admitted that the UK
OL,19,FGovernment has a "long way to go" on
OL,20,Ftackling drugs in prisons like Parc.
