OL,6,FThe Director of HMP Parc, Will Styles,
OL,7,Ftold MPs that security checks on staff
OL,8,Fhave increased five-fold since June
OL,9,Fbut that the vast majority of staff
OL,10,Fare not corrupt and not the source of
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,FHe said that "There are a number of
OL,14,Fingress routes for contraband into
OL,15,Fprisons. It can be thrown over the
OL,16,Fwall. It can be brought in by visitors
OL,17,Fsecreted in their bodily offices or in
OL,18,Fchildren's nappies, etc, when they
OL,19,Fcome to social visits with their loved
OL,20,Fones.
