OL,6,F"Staff corruption is an issue in many
OL,7,Fprisons, and one of the key ingress
OL,8,Froutes certainly experienced at Parc
OL,9,Fare kind of industrial-specification
OL,10,Fdrone drops organised by organised
OL,11,Fcrime gangs, in our case, organised
OL,12,Fcrime gangs, which we think are
OL,13,Fcentred around Wales and the Midlands."
OL,15,FMr Styles also told MPs that staffing
OL,16,Flevels had increased as had security
OL,17,Fchecks and he was convinced that Parc
OL,18,Fis a safe prison.
